Maintainer: Carlos Vergara-Hernández <vergara_car@gva.es>
Description: Call 'WinBUGS' or 'OpenBUGS' from your R session running multiple chains
    in parallel. Results are returned in an object of class 'bugs' and 'pbugs'. 
    Functions have been adapted from the 'R2WinBUGS' package (Sturtz, Ligges and Gelman, 2005 <DOI:10.18637/jss.v012.i03>).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: no
SystemRequirements: WinBUGS (1.4.3) or OpenBUGS (>= 3.2.3)
URL: https://github.com/fisabio/pbugs
BugReports: https://github.com/fisabio/pbugs/issues
